snippet.title: CLOSED HANDS - LAUNCH TEASER
snippet.description:
CLOSED HANDS is a groundbreaking work of interactive fiction by PASSENGER. The full game will be released for Windows/Mac/Linux on 05/03/2021 with digital partners HOME MCR. Proudly supported by Arts Council England.

More info: 
http://closed-hands.com

Follow PASSENGER: http://twitter.com/PASSENGERGAMES
